{"tid":1516089,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"質疑中共獲貸款助逼害新疆人 美議員要求世銀調查","createTime":"2019-08-29T12:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T12:53:32.000Z","uid":68738,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c692eedbfa01ccdefe8408ddbe4a3305e0ae51","tid":1516089,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190829/large/1567068445_1996.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190829%2Flarge%2F1567068445_1996.jpg&h=79efa008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中共向世界銀行貸款，在新疆興建再教育營。(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n美國國會及行政當局中國委員會的議員近日去信世銀行長馬爾帕斯（David Malpass），質疑世銀向中共貸款，在新疆建立「再教育營」，殘害新疆的維吾爾族人，議員要求世銀進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n美國參議院參議員盧比奧（Senator Rubio）與眾議員麥戈文（Jim McGovern）聯名去信馬爾帕斯，指世銀在2015年批准一筆5,000萬美元（約3.9萬億港元）的貸款，中方宣稱是用作「為新疆近4.9萬青年改善職業技術教育和就業機會」，實際上是興建關押逾100萬維吾爾族人的再教育營。<br />\n<br />\n盧比奧與麥戈文在信中表示對這筆貸款的用途表示擔憂，指越來越多證據顯示，維族人被關在再教育營是要進行控制和灌輸政治思想，涉及虐待和折磨，同時要求他們從事強制勞動，強迫他們放棄宗教和文化。被扣留更強迫與子女分開，小童則被送到禁止使用母語及文化的寄宿學校或孤兒院。我們認為，這種行為，可能構成中共對維吾爾族和其它少數民族犯下危害人類罪。<br />\n<br />\n議員要求世銀調查這筆貸款的真正用途，同時要求世銀停止這筆貸款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190829/59986675?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190829%2F59986675%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkN9ps0HX4IqOCTpD1RfAd9E%3D&h=fa7d7119\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190829%2F59986675%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=a6587ae7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190829/59986675?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"f05bea23a9a9aea6c3c2673f99c33a50e5edef35","tid":1516089,"uid":95520,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:16:21.000Z","msg":"終於搞到新疆?"},{"pid":"634354e17e8c625d388014ffa168420cbc0b6077","tid":1516089,"uid":54303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:16:54.000Z","msg":"係咪有間新疆公司想上市？要阻止！"},{"pid":"90393ac86625476dd573763c3d4c2fa4c75f7500","tid":1516089,"uid":31151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:19:18.000Z","msg":"問世銀借錢搞集中營仲要得美國發現 成班真係碌柒黎"},{"pid":"0c715c231db0ed26ca6e0a49d3e98a55fcc08177","tid":1516089,"uid":1086,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:19:40.000Z","msg":"好撚野<br />\n問世界借錢搞集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8647f8c71018389b170cbe56545c2ede67cf38","tid":1516089,"uid":15696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:19:54.000Z","msg":"為新疆近4.9萬青年改善職業技術教育和就業機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9c9ea46a3f724edc3755fdd629a4b57b7204af","tid":1516089,"uid":78470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:20:50.000Z","msg":"rubio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb8af3d143357648ec3bf8031b952cce62aad07","tid":1516089,"uid":42554,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:21:20.000Z","msg":"乜天朝冇錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d9050f59917617e3ab5af8d8668a3ae7c0ab1e","tid":1516089,"uid":31655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a